<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"style":{"color":{"text":"#632f91"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#632f91"><strong>Supporting OVW TA Providers</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"constrained","contentSize":"200px"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:image {"align":"center","id":16186,"sizeSlug":"medium","linkDestination":"none","className":"is-style-default"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-medium is-style-default"><img src="https://ldev.ta2ta.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Weave-with-4-OVW-Providers-300x297.png" alt="TA2TA Logo Alternate Shorten" class="wp-image-16186"/></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center">TA2TA: The TA Providerâ€™s Resource Center (TA2TA) supports OVW TA projects through this website by hosting a calendar of OVW-funded in-person and online educational events, a directory of OVWâ€™s TA providers, a library of resources developed by OVW TA providers, webinars designed specifically for OVW TA providers, and a new grantee orientation page for OVWâ€™s Training and Technical Assistance (TTA) Program.</p>
